#new conda env requires installation of all packages else other packages from outside are taken: ipython+jupyter+


jupyter_notebook_config.py is run when the notebook server starts, not when a kernel starts. The kernel startup is up to IPython (for Python kernels).



We use in jupyter session py35 and py27 environments from conda.

  503  conda create -n py355 python=3.5 ipykernel
  504  conda create -n py277 python=2.7 ipykernel

py355: 
	pip install jupyter
pip install git+https://github.com/fherwig/nupy
conda install nb_conda_kernels

py277
pip install git+https://github.com/fherwig/nupy
pip install matplotlib
pip install scipy
pip install h5py
pip install JSAnimation



  534  conda install -c conda-forge ipywidgets
  535  jupyter-nbextension enable --py --sys-prefix widgetsnbextension
